    <patterns>
      <pattern name="Intent-metadata decoration" location="src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/conversation/SoftSlashRouter.ts (new)">
        Export `decorateMessage(intent: Intent, message: ChatMessage): ChatMessage`. Adds `commandIntent: 'summarize' | 'draft' | 'extract-entities' | 'analyze'` metadata. BFF chat endpoint reads this in existing payload schema; CapabilityRouter Layer 1 consumes.
      </pattern>
