    <criterion testable="true">`/summarize #file.docx` composes correctly: intent has both command + reference; BFF payload includes both.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">NFR-01 preserved: agent still conversational after a soft-slash invocation (follow-up message receives conversational response).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">NFR-11 preserved: natural-language "summarize this" still works via existing CapabilityRouter.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Telemetry per ADR-015 — command name only, no user message text logged.</criterion>
